window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Riding shotgun to face my boyfriend wasn't exactly on my bingo card...<br> Especially when the man behind the wheel is the one my boyfriend demanded I cut ties with.<br> Griffin Thorne is LAU's hockey captain, my brother's best friend, and my roommate.<br> He's also the only person I can rely on at the moment, even though he hates me after I followed through my boyfriend's...<i>suggestion</i>.<br> To be fair, I get it.<br> Why he hates me.<br> In a way, I hate me too.<br> But as long as this impromptu road trip stays our little secret, everything will be fine.<br> Maybe.<br> Hopefully.<br> Okay, let's be honest.<br> If my boyfriend doesn't kill me for sharing a room with Griffin Thorne, my brother will.<br> <br> <b>Tropes:</b><br> Forced Proximity<br> Brother's Best Friend<br> Forbidden Romance<br> He Falls First<br> One Bed<br> Hockey Romance</p>"; 
